original_query: Query 1: List the specifications of iphone 13 max and iphone 16 max in a markdown table

iphone_13_max_specs.text: The iPhone 13 Pro Max (2021) features a Ceramic Shield front, textured matte glass back, and stainless steel design. Available in Graphite, Gold, Silver, Sierra Blue, and Alpine Green, it offers 128GB, 256GB, 512GB, or 1TB storage. It measures 3.07" x 6.33" x 0.30", weighing 8.46 ounces. The 6.7" Super Retina XDR display with ProMotion (2778x1284 at 458 ppi, up to 120Hz) has a 2,000,000:1 contrast ratio and 1000-1200 nits brightness. It's rated IP68. Powered by the A15 Bionic chip (6-core CPU, 5-core GPU, 16-core Neural Engine), it has a Pro 12MP camera system (Telephoto f/2.8, Wide f/1.5, Ultra Wide f/1.8 with 120° FOV), offering 3x optical zoom in, 2x out, and up to 15x digital zoom, plus features like Night mode, Apple ProRAW, and Cinematic mode for video (1080p at 30 fps), and Dolby Vision HDR up to 4K at 60 fps, and ProRes video up to 4k at 30 fps.
